<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَتَجِبُ عِدَّةُ الوَفَاةِ فِي المَنْزِلِ حَيْثُ وَجَبَتْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَإِنْ تَحَوَّلَتْ خَوْفاً، أَوْ قَهْراً،<span class="c5"> أَوْ لِحَقٍّ:</span> انْتَقَلَتْ حَيْثُ شَاءَتْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلَهَا الخُرُوجُ لِحَاجَتِهَا نَهَاراً، لَا لَيْلاً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَإِنْ تَرَكَتِ الإِحْدَادَ:</span> أَثِمَتْ، وَتَمَّتْ عِدَّتُهَا بِمُضِيِّ زَمَانِهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>